><strong>I.</strong></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Let me tell you a story.&nbsp;</p><p style=
=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"=
>Imagine you&#8217;re a cattle rancher in the high plains of Colorado.&nbsp=
;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
: 0 0 1em 0;">You rent a small plot of land from a neighbor. You have twent=
y head of cattle.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; lin=
e-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">You tell folks about how you came to Co=
lorado from out East when you were fourteen, working a construction gig wit=
h your dad. You fell in love with horses and cattle and the lifestyle of ra=
nching here. You decided to stay.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size:=
 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">You&#8217;re hoping to buy yo=
ur own land one day, and expand the small herd you have. Maybe you&#8217;ll=
 explore regenerative grazing.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">But to do that, you need to get =
your books in order. You get by, but your margins are thin. You need a busi=
ness plan to give to your bank. Not to mention a balance sheet.</p><p style=
=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"=
>You&#8217;re working on it. But it&#8217;s hard to find time at the very e=
nd of your days, when you&#8217;ve been outside and one of your pups went m=
issing and so you had to drive over to the neighbors&#8217; to find him and=
 then one of the cows gave birth when you got back.</p><p style=3D"color: #=
1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">You know th=
e government has programs that will help you grow your ranch, but the appli=
cations are lengthy and hard to keep track of.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1=
a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Not to mention t=
hat just to stay compliant as a rancher, you&#8217;re probably filing paper=
work for six &#8211; <em>or is it seven?</em> &#8211; different government =
agencies.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">You love your job, and you need to do all this to do =
your job. But all this means wiping the cow crap off your hands, going on t=
he computer, and hunting through slow-loading government websites. One of t=
hem took 25 minutes to download a PDF last week. You made lunch in the mean=
time.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; ma=
rgin: 0 0 1em 0;">Farm accounting, farm funding, farm compliance. There&#82=
17;s paperwork for everything it seems. Hours and hours a week of paperwork=
=2E</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-s=
ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
: 0 0 1em 0;">And you&#8217;re worried about things happening around the wo=
rld, outside your control. Drought and wildfires from climate change have w=
racked Colorado of late. Supply chains still backed up from the pandemic. R=
ising fertilizer and fuel costs from the war with Russia. Inflation making =
everything worse.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">This rancher is real &#8211; and his name is =
Teo.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; mar=
gin: 0 0 1em 0;">Teo is one of Ambrook&#8217;s early customers. We helped h=
im get a farm grant during the pandemic, when the rodeos were shut down and=
 the meat processing facilities were backed up. Now he&#8217;s using Ambroo=
k to get his books in order and business plan in place.</p><p style=3D"colo=
r: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">This is=
 Teo&#8217;s story, and the story of countless producers across the country=
=2E Some folks move into farming, like Te=
o. Many have been farming for their =
whole lives. The paperwork sucks all the same.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1=
a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><strong>II.</str=
ong>&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26p=
x; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Now, let me tell you my story.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"=
color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">I g=
rew up with conversations about agriculture at the dinner table.&nbsp;</p><=
p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 =
